        <p style="font-style:italic;font-size:15px;margin-top:12px;max-width:700px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto">The two traditions describe the same eschatological geography and sequence from opposing theological loyalties. Whether this reflects prophetic identity or polemical construction cannot be resolved by evidence alone ŌĆö it requires a prior commitment about the nature of prophecy itself. The question is not closed. Watch carefully.</p>
